<h2>Think deeply. Act justly.</h2>
<div class='widget-content'>
<a href='http://core-ethics.com'>
<img alt='Think deeply. Act justly.' height='200' id='Image1_img' src='http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-wVkyTbvSHJE/WjfhD7zpBBI/AAAAAAAAJPg/YVteC8n707AYSp-kAxFhLM3hM-l6Rga0QCK4BGAYYCw/s1600/FinalLogo-cropped-01PhiSwordJPG.jpg' width='200'/>
